by Andonov|Bobi Andonov]] || {{n/a|Non-album single}} || \"Smoke\" || [[Bobby Andonov]], [[Sam Watters|Samuel Watters]], [[Louis Biancaniello]], Dylan William\n|-\n| [[Seeb (music producers)|SeeB]] || ''[[Nice to Meet You (Seeb EP)|Nice to Meet You EP]]'' || \"Drink About\"<br>{{small|(featuring [[Dagny (singer)|Dagny]])}} || [[Seeb (music producers)|Simen Eriksrud]], [[Seeb (music producers)|Espen Borg]], Joakim Haukaas, [[Alex Hope (songwriter)|Alex Hope]], [[Kid Harpoon|Thomas Hull]]\n|-\n| [[Alina Baraz]] || ''The Color of You'' || \"Tainted\" || [[Alina Baraz]], [[Stint (producer)|Ajay Bhattacharya]]\n|-\n| [[The Rubens]] || ''[[Lo La Ru]]'' ||style=\"background:#6495ed\"| \"[[Never Ever (The Rubens song)|Never Ever]]\"<br>{{small|(featuring Sarah)}} || [[The Rubens|Samuel Margin]], [[The Rubens|Elliott Margin]]\n|-\n| [[Peking Duk]] || ''[[Reprisal (EP)|Reprisal EP]]'' ||style=\"background:#87ceeb\"|  \"[[Fire (Peking Duk song)|Fire]]\" || [[Peking Duk|Adan Hyde]], [[Peking Duk|Reuben Styles]], [[Sam Littlemore|Samuel Littlemore]]\n|-\n| [[Lykke Li]] || ''[[So Sad So Sexy]]'' || \"Sex Money Feelings Die\" || [[Lykke Li|Li Zachrisson]], [[Ilsey Juber]], [[Malay (record producer)|James Ryan Ho]], [[DJ Dahi|Dacoury Natche]], [[Kid Harpoon|Thomas Hull]]\n|-\n| [[Ruel (singer)|Ruel]] || ''[[Ready (Ruel EP)|Ready EP]]'' ||style=\"background:#ffffcc\"| \"[[Younger (Ruel song)|Younger]]\" || [[Ruel (singer)|Ruel van Dijk]], [[M-Phazes|Mark Landon]], [[Symbolyc One|Larry Griffin Jr.]], JaVohn Griffin\n|-\n| [[Cosmo's Midnight]] || ''What Comes Next'' || \"Talk to Me\"<br>{{small|(featuring [[Tove Styrke]])}} || [[Cosmo's Midnight|Cosmo Liney]], [[Cosmo's Midnight|Patrick Liney]]\n|-\n| [[Ruel (singer)|Ruel]] || ''[[Ready (Ruel EP)|Ready EP]]'' || \"Intro\" || [[Ruel (singer)|Ruel van Dijk]], [[M-Phazes|Mark Landon]], [[Symbolyc One|Larry Griffin Jr.]]\n|-\n| [[Odette (musician)|Odette]] || ''To a Stranger'' || \"Lights On\" || [[Odette (musician)|Georgia Sallybanks]], 