 Kleinman]], [[Michael Uzowuru]], [[Rodaidh McDonald]], William Boston\n|-\n| rowspan=\"23\"| 2019 || [[Maren Morris]] || ''[[Girl (Maren Morris album)|Girl]]'' || \"[[Girl (Maren Morris song)|Girl]]\" || [[Maren Morris]], [[Greg Kurstin]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Meg Mac]] || rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Hope (Meg Mac album)|Hope]]'' || \"Something Tells Me\" || [[Meg Mac|Megan McInerney]]\n|-\n| \"Head Away\" || [[Meg Mac|Megan McInerney]]\n|-\n| [[Maren Morris]] || ''[[Girl (Maren Morris album)|Girl]]'' || \"Common\"<br>{{small|(featuring [[Brandi Carlile]])}} || [[Maren Morris]], [[Greg Kurstin]]\n|-\n| [[John Legend]] || {{TBA}} ||style=\"background:#ffffcc\"| \"Preach\" || [[John Legend|John Stephens]], [[Greg Kurstin]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"| [[Khalid (singer)|Khalid]] || rowspan=\"4\"| ''[[Free Spirit (Khalid album)|Free Spirit]]'' || \"Paradise\" || [[Khalid (singer)|Khalid Robinson]], [[John Hill (record producer)|Jonathan Hill]], [[DJ Dahi|Dacoury Natche]]\n|-\n| \"Outta My Head\"<br>{{small|(with [[John Mayer]])}} || [[Khalid (singer)|Khalid Robinson]], [[John Mayer]], Jamil Chammas, [[John Hill (record producer)|Jonathan Hill]]\n|-\n| \"Free Spirit\" || [[Khalid (singer)|Khalid Robinson]], Ryan Vojtesak, Jamil Chammas, Justin Scott Lucas\n|-\n| \"Bluffin'\" || [[Khalid (singer)|Khalid Robinson]], Ryan Vojtesak, Jamil Chammas\n|-\n| Miquela || {{n/a|Non-album single}} || \"Right Back\" || Miquela Sousak, Ethan Snoreck, Jordan Palmer\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Ruel (singer)|Ruel]] || rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Free Time (EP)|Free Time]]'' || \"[[Real Thing (Ruel song)]]\" || [[Ruel (singer)|Ruel van Dijk]], [[M-Phazes|Mark Landon]]\n|-\n|style=\"background:#ffffcc\"| \"[[Painkiller (Ruel song)|Painkiller]]\" || [[Ruel (singer)|Ruel van Dijk]], [[M-Phazes|Mark Landon]]\n|-\n| [[Jonas Brothers]] || ''[[Happiness Begins]]'' || \"Happy When I'm Sad\" || [[Jonas Brothers|Nicholas Jonas]], [[Joel Little]]\n|-\n| [[Mabel (singer)|Mabel]] || ''[[High Expectations]]'' || \"FML\" || [[Mabel (singer)|Mabel McVey]], Kelly Kiara, [[Marlon Roudette|Marlon McVey-Roudette]], [[Pop & Oak|Warren Felder]]\n|-\n|[[Hilltop Hoods]] || ''[[The Great Expanse]]'' || \"Exit Sign\" ||  \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Foster the People]] || rowspan=\"2\"| ''Pick U Up EP'' || \"Imagination\" || \n|-\n| \"Pick U Up\" || \n|-\n|[[Kaskade]] || {{n/a|Non-album single}} || \"[[With You (Kaskade and Meghan Trainor song)|With You]]\"<br>{{small|(with [[Meghan Trainor]])}} || [[Kaskade|Ryan Raddon]], [[Finn Bjarnson]], [[Bynon|Richard Beynon]], [[Project 46|Thomas Shaw]], [[Kuya Productions|Samuel Gerongco]], [[Kuya Productions|Robert Gerongco]]\n|-\n|[[Ingrid Michaelson]] || ''[[Stranger Songs]]'' || \"Pretty\" ||  [[Ingrid Michaelson]], [[Alex Hope (songwriter)|Alexandra Robotham]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Gallant (singer)|Gallant]] || rowspan=\"2\"| ''Sweet Insomnia'' || \"Crimes\" || [[Gallant (singer)|Christopher Gallant]], [[Stint (producer)|Ajay Bhattacharya]], Benjamin Abraham\n|-\n| \"Celine\" || \n|-\n| [[Cashmere Cat]] || ''[[Princess Catgirl]]'' || \"Without You\" || [[Cashmere Cat|Magnus August Hoiberg]], [[Benny Blanco|Benjamin Levin]], Kevin Esmenda, [[Julia Michaels]], [[Justin Tranter]], [[Mattman & Robin|Mattias Larsson]], [[Mattman & Robin|Robin Fredriksson]], [[Oscar Holter]]\n|-\n|[[Bea Miller]] || {{n/a|Non-album single}} || \"Never Gonna Like You\"<br>{{small|(featuring [[Snakehips (duo)|Snakehips]])}} || [[Snakehips (duo)|Oliver Dickinson]], [[Snakehips (duo)|James David]], [[Joe Janiak]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2020 || [[Halsey (singer)|Halsey]] || ''[[Manic (album)|Manic]]'' || \"I Hate Everybody\" || [[Halsey (singer)|Ashley Frangipane]], [[Noonie Bao]], [[Lido (musician)|Peder Losneg\u00e5rd]], [[Benny Blanco|Benjamin Levin]], [[Cashmere Cat|Magnus August H\u00f8iberg]], Nathan Perez, [[Finneas O'Connell]]\n|-\n|[[SZA (singer)|SZA]], [[Justin Timberlake]]\n|TROLLS: World Tour\n(Original Motion Picture Soundtrack)\n|\"The Other Side\"\n|[[Ludwig G\u00f6ransson]]