 Open|Australian Open]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| A$270,000 || $260,871\n|-\n| 3.||[[2014 ABN AMRO World Tennis Tournament|Rotterdam Open]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u20ac34,085 || $307,141\n|-\n| 4.||[[2014 Abierto Mexicano Telcel|Mexican Open]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| $67,570 || $374,711\n|-\n| 5.||[[2014 BNP Paribas Open|Indian Wells Masters]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| $52,000 || $426,711\n|-\n| 6.||[[2014 Sony Open Tennis|Miami Masters]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| $98,130 || $524,841\n|-\n| 7.||[[2014 Mutua Madrid Open|Mutua Madrid Open]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u20ac45,530 || $587,666\n|-\n| 8.||[[2014 Internazionali BNL d'Italia|Italian Open]]|| style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u20ac68,890 || $682,438\n|-\n| 9.||[[2014 French Open|French Open]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u20ac412,500 || $1,244,428\n|-\n| 10.||[[2014 Aegon Championships|Queen's Club Championships]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u20ac10,160 || $1,258,803\n|-\n| 11.||[[2014 Wimbledon Championships|Wimbledon Championships]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| \u00a3226,000 || $1,643,184\n|-\n| 12.||[[2014 Rogers Cup|Canadian Open]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| $75,155 || $1,718,339\n|-\n| 13.||[[2014 Western & Southern Open|Cincinnati Masters]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| $80,165 || $1,798,504\n|-\n| 14.||[[2014 US Open (tennis)|US Open]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| $370,250 || $2,168,754\n|-\n| 15.||'''[[2014 ATP Shenzhen Open|Shenzhen Open]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| '''$106,970 || '''$2,275,724\n|-\n| 16.||[[2014 China Open (tennis)|China Open]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| $129,000 || $2,404,724\n|-\n| 17.||[[2014 Shanghai Rolex Masters|Shanghai Masters]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"| $52,035||$2,456,759\n|-\n| 18.||'''[[2014 Erste Bank Open|Vienna Open]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"| '''\u20ac94,500||'''$2,576,094\n|-\n| 19.||'''[[2014 Valencia Open 500|Valencia Open]]||style=\"text-align:center;\"| '''\u20ac390,3